LOCATION:BISD Administration Building, 801 S. Ennis St., Bryan
DESCRIPTION:HELD 6/15: board unanimously adopted a balanced FY2026-27 budget with no tax-rate change and no use of reserves; also named 3 principals. Tracker BV-0049/0050.
