DTSTAMP:20260615T120000Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260625
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260626
SUMMARY:College Station City Council regular meeting (HELD)
DESCRIPTION:HELD 6/25: consent agenda approved unanimously (Axon $401K body-camera change order; Barron/Decatur signal $372,872; polymer $315K); 2.5-hr Northgate workshop, no vote; CIP update (69 projects, $474.6M). Tracker BV-0061..BV-0065. Confidence: Reported.
END:VEVENT
