DTSTART;TZID=America/Chicago:20260623T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Chicago:20260623T120000
SUMMARY:Brazos County Commissioners Court (HELD)
LOCATION:Brazos County Administration Building, 200 S. Texas Ave., Bryan
DESCRIPTION:HELD 6/23: adopted a countywide AI policy (human oversight); acted on a compensation study (up to 10% for ~17% below-market staff); Public Defender quarterly report (612 clients, 4 of 10 attorney vacancies); screwworm public-awareness response. Tracker BV-0066..BV-0069. Confidence: Reported.
END:VEVENT
